去「夕陽紅」，很多老年人在門口哭。他們和他一樣將辛辛苦苦積攢一輩的血汗錢全投進去了。為這個事，還把腿給摔斷了，他希望當地政府能管管這事。<br />\n<br />\n當地雁峰區委網信辦對老人的留言回應稱：他的留言已收到，反映的情況已轉交相關部門核實處理。<br />\n<br />\n原文係咁..礦工係邊單"},{"pid":"1830d824cad1559bfad5a0cc2ed090c8fe498796","tid":1781553,"uid":46947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"藍屍廢老話齋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n行得正企得正，好人好姐做乜要出嚟抗議攪攪震攪亂社會。"},{"pid":"b78ee2c033fc2a8c3e0583e47ce93d7b4dd9b138","tid":1781553,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"之後會越來越頻密"},{"pid":"8338c45192a8682666cb99427bf4c6579e335b49","tid":1781553,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/09/12-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F12-7.jpg&h=7e4ac4d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/l7ar8K20QQI/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fl7ar8K20QQI%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=1afb231a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/04/537d0c6edefdbf5b449ddedec1d00417-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F537d0c6edefdbf5b449ddedec1d00417-600x400.jpg&h=82ee6153&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2470cd13671ff99d9f5b474060e24ecdfa97b0ae","tid":1781553,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"6億之嘛<br />\n叫愛國愛黨香港警察分d ot錢番去咪解決晒囉"},{"pid":"66658b2bc129dc2b489e274519612b11ebd99603","tid":1781553,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"6億？關稅都畀唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}